snippet.title: Taiko Frenzy - Mixed Reality Update
snippet.description:
The Mixed Reality Update for Taiko Frenzy is coming on Meta Quest App Lab. Introducing a new passthrough feature.

Taiko Frenzy is a VR rhythm game set in a stunning, colorful scenery for Meta Quest 2. Immerse yourself in the world of Japanese folklore with original soundtracks exclusively composed for the game.

Download it for free on App Lab: https://ocul.us/3oq1nNR
